Vim Configs

Install:
    git clone git@github.com:zirrostig/dotvim.git ~/.vim
    cd ~/.vim
    git submodule init
    git submodule update
    ln -s ~/.vim/vimrc ~/.vimrc

Command-T Install:
    cd ~/.vim/bundle/command-t
    bundle install
    rake make

    From vim:
        :call pathogen#helptags()

Notes:
    I can now do my job
